org.apache.juddi.api.impl.rest

Class UDDIInquiryJAXRS

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juddi.api.impl.rest.UDDIInquiryJAXRS

  • @Path(value="/")
 @Produces(value={"application/xml","application/json","text/html"})
public class UDDIInquiryJAXRS
extends Object
    UDDI Inquiry functions via a JAX-RS REST API. It's basically a wrapper for the REST fans to access UDDI from a URL pattern This class will ONLY deploy using the Apache CXF WS stack for REST (JAX-RS)
    Author:
    Alex O'Ree
